nodes.text: Mok's Cheap Eats was a restaurant in The Works on Coruscant, catering to factory workers.

It was during a meeting there in 32 BBY that Naboo Senator Palpatine and Jedi Master Dooku agreed to work together to tear down the Galactic Republic so that it could be rebuilt, and Dooku informed Palpatine that Anakin Skywalker might be the Chosen One.
